snippet.title: Sirocco Thugs : Winds of Pain - Gameplay Showcase
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam : https://store.steampowered.com/app/3042790/Sirocco_Thugs__Winds_of_Pain/

Roundhouse Kicks, Six shooters and rusty Lead Pipes become your vehicles for revenge against the Don.... 

Grab some scrap and engage in brutal, breakneck melee combat in this FPS Beat 'Em Up!
